{"tid":105792,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"不要神化菲林攝影，它不是想像中美好","createTime":"2017-02-03T07:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T10:42:04.000Z","uid":81211,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a18ec6b331e917a6847f4782258f76f2cc8656","tid":105792,"uid":81211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"(編按︰來自國外網站 Photo Focus 的攝影師 Scott Bourne，撰寫了一篇關於菲林攝影的文章，引起了網友的熱話。以下是有關內文的要點翻譯，大家不妨參考及思考一下。)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/pics03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F04%2Fpics03.jpg&h=720864b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nScott Bourne︰<br />\n<br />\n我有時發現，人們對於菲林攝影有種過度狂熱的吹捧，這是源於一些誤解。<br />\n<br />\n如果你很年輕，出生於這個數碼年代，很自然就會美化那些你從未經歷過的舊日子。我比起大多數年輕人拍攝過更多菲林，數碼攝影只是我職業生命裏的後期才出現，我用菲林拍攝比起數碼攝影還多。我用菲林、每天都拍、以此維生，而它並不是那麼美好。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，Tri-X 是有顆粒的，而且你用 ISO 400 的時候，雜訊就像現在用 ISO 25,600 一樣的多。而回想當日，根本沒甚麼人會談「低光表現」，因為那跟本稱不上表現。<br />\n<br />\n而且沒有 Photoshop、沒有 HDR、沒有接合式全景影像，一旦犯錯你就完了，因為底片後製員很難找，而且可以補救的也沒有那麼多，並且費用高昂手工很慢。基本上，你一定要在相機內完美地拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n菲林很昂貴，而沖曬則更加昂貴，並且在沖曬顯影的過程，會用到很多對環境有害的物質，很多用過的重金屬，到今天仍然破壞我們的生態。<br />\n<br />\n你也很難從菲林製出大型的照片，如果你的照片要用於出版印刷，你就要使用非常昂貴的掃描器，並且質素也不一定好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/pics02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F04%2Fpics02.jpg&h=bea26429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我還能列出其他問題，但重點是菲林並不那麼美好。「難以使用並不代表作品會更好」，無論你花幾多工夫去拍攝一張照片，那並不代表影像就自然變得更美好，那依然只是一張照片。<br />\n<br />\n有些「藝術家」會覺得「過程比結果更重要」，他們有自由去這樣想，但我知道即使我盡全力去把所有事做妥，而拍攝依然出問題時，至少在數碼年代我可以用後製去善後，如果你依然堅持「過程」，那麼很有可能你不是去製作好的影像。使用菲林並不令你成為藝術家，工具並不重要，真正重要的是洞見、心思、技藝的純熟、出色的故事、對於拍攝對象的關懷與熱情，這些才會令你成為藝術家。<br />\n<br />\n過程只是工具，你越快完成到，就越快可以再前進。100年後人們再看你的照片，會說「嘩！這是 Tri-X」嗎？不會，只有影像才有價值。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/212881tone12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F04%2F212881tone12.jpg&h=8bbf2030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 四年前高登攝影台曾經討論過依個問題，今日大家睇法有沒咩改變"},{"pid":"99d0e45868acf32ac013748360833c20ae29766a","tid":105792,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"依個咪係當做興趣既人同真係用黎搵食既人心態既分別"},{"pid":"dbbad11cae577901cf0ddf6b3759ebd145926c14","tid":105792,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:28:43.000Z","msg":"同樣構圖既女仔包面相<br />\n數碼：屌你唔識影相架？<br />\n菲林：好有味道呀"},{"pid":"84ac71dc7acd155c3c0b47a9630f9420725f16ad","tid":105792,"uid":45568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"同意的，但正因為有種種規限限制了攝影時的方便，會有更多時間構思，會思考按快門一刻的意義。<br />\n我平時都有影底片，不過只會在我想做一些有特別意義的題材時才會用，底片只是工具的一種，工具沒有分好壞，只有用途。"},{"pid":"28122b2e36a517485f5746e9151b6c2a85a3ef14","tid":105792,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"菲林味呢句野真係無撚敵<br />\n同空氣感立體感有得比<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d317ebe6725137bf58881149c27b7d7bf953e06","tid":105792,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同意的，但正因為有種種規限限制了攝影時的方便，會有更多時間構思，會思考按快門一刻的意義。<br />\n我平時都有影底片，不過只會在我想做一些有特別意義的題材時才會用，底片只是工具的一種，工具沒有分好壞，只有用途。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n菲林同cf/sd....咭，都只是一個media。（我覺得唔係工具）<br />\n<br />\n不過，菲林這個media有個性，唔一定會好忠於原本咁記錄影像。<br />\n咭呢：佢會照足你相機setting記錄，點推張相，唔係相機，唔係張咭，係你。<br />\n<br />\n講方便/成本當然就一面倒。"},{"pid":"4b898af361c5b4e9f1b8ee1eaf6109fed25637de","tid":105792,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菲林味呢句野真係無撚敵<br />\n同空氣感立體感有得比<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「菲林味」都係講色調同顆粒，識用Lightroom話咁易整<br />\n<br />\n「立體感」就真有其事，由清晰至到散景既過渡越smooth越立體，留意下Leica鏡影既相就知咩叫立體。<br />\n<br />\n至於「空氣感」就到今日都唔知係咩撚1999"},{"pid":"78c12d13c07f46eced5e61958468af401d8d42cb","tid":105792,"uid":74302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"我而家都冇玩菲林了<br />\n單反都少用<br />\n見到唔少人用佢來當好型 好特別咁。覺得嘔心。<br />\n但可以延續到呢樣野都好既"},{"pid":"9b7644767d51a5feef3a5e41ac1cace828fad3d0","tid":105792,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"難以使用並不代表作品會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b42fa2898537c58809384033427e1119aa5a71","tid":105792,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:45:27.000Z","msg":"重要都係呢句：<span style=\"color: red;\">工具並不重要，真正重要的是洞見、心思、技藝的純熟、出色的故事、對於拍攝對象的關懷與熱情</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實呢d道理同呀媽係女人一樣咁簡單，係人都知，除左器材撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支鏡有奶味就代表影相勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eaac37f6fc0ae27a468582a72742b5199cbddc2","tid":105792,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>菲林味呢句野真係無撚敵<br />\n同空氣感立體感有得比<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「菲林味」都係講色調同顆粒，識用Lightroom話咁易整<br />\n<br />\n「立體感」就真有其事，由清晰至到散景既過渡越smooth越立體，留意下Leica鏡影既相就知咩叫立體。<br />\n<br />\n至於「空氣感」就到今日都唔知係咩撚1999</blockquote><br />\n空氣感。光，少野，低對比，總知就係空氣感"},{"pid":"9ca39a93846b519b97a8df0bb71eb45187af5904","tid":105792,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>菲林味呢句野真係無撚敵<br />\n同空氣感立體感有得比<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「菲林味」都係講色調同顆粒，識用Lightroom話咁易整<br />\n<br />\n「立體感」就真有其事，由清晰至到散景既過渡越smooth越立體，留意下Leica鏡影既相就知咩叫立體。<br />\n<br />\n至於「空氣感」就到今日都唔知係咩撚1999</blockquote><br />\n空氣感。光，少野，低對比，總知就係空氣感</blockquote><br />\n有沒相睇下，我都係第一次聽依個term"},{"pid":"dc8f54e4adddd70a5ffff95fc4c367a717ed72bd","tid":105792,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>菲林味呢句野真係無撚敵<br />\n同空氣感立體感有得比<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「菲林味」都係講色調同顆粒，識用Lightroom話咁易整<br />\n<br />\n「立體感」就真有其事，由清晰至到散景既過渡越smooth越立體，留意下Leica鏡影既相就知咩叫立體。<br />\n<br />\n至於「空氣感」就到今日都唔知係咩撚1999</blockquote><br />\n空氣感。光，少野，低對比，總知就係空氣感</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48G3711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48G3711.jpg&h=b5cf2c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想知咩係藍調相多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e51b525713aec79eca470b55fef260b95c63c3d","tid":105792,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「菲林味」都係講色調同顆粒，識用Lightroom話咁易整<br />\n<br />\n「立體感」就真有其事，由清晰至到散景既過渡越smooth越立體，留意下Leica鏡影既相就知咩叫立體。<br />\n<br />\n至於「空氣感」就到今日都唔知係咩撚1999</blockquote><br />\n空氣感。光，少野，低對比，總知就係空氣感</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48G3711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48G3711.jpg&h=b5cf2c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想知咩係藍調相多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/928237b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F928237b.jpg&h=0e62d689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夠藍未？"},{"pid":"9477aff424c6a7d4fb4682e99f741e3aee2f1bb2","tid":105792,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「菲林味」都係講色調同顆粒，識用Lightroom話咁易整<br />\n<br />\n「立體感」就真有其事，由清晰至到散景既過渡越smooth越立體，留意下Leica鏡影既相就知咩叫立體。<br />\n<br />\n至於「空氣感」就到今日都唔知係咩撚1999</blockquote><br />\n空氣感。光，少野，低對比，總知就係空氣感</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48G3711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48G3711.jpg&h=b5cf2c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想知咩係藍調相多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜有人會留意呢條on9仔"},{"pid":"d4b6486882c01b6deeb7aa483205b945e5412abe","tid":105792,"uid":3811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:07:02.000Z","msg":"神化菲林既人同比成皮野買a7但插幾百蚊貨仔老鏡既人一樣"},{"pid":"313ece6033ccc241fe3a5e55a6283dc29d2181df","tid":105792,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n空氣感。光，少野，低對比，總知就係空氣感</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48G3711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48G3711.jpg&h=b5cf2c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想知咩係藍調相多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜有人會留意呢條on9仔</blockquote><br />\n至少連你都留意"},{"pid":"67e84674f9841e5121f5e6ecf0514621c1d24ec7","tid":105792,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:08:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n空氣感。光，少野，低對比，總知就係空氣感</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48G3711.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48G3711.jpg&h=b5cf2c64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想知咩係藍調相多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜有人會留意呢條on9仔</blockquote><br />\n同卐卐有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa976fdbf2dc4761e28b04e85026047dea81a2c","tid":105792,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T09:29:45.000Z","msg